author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Novavax Inc says positive top-line data from RSV F-protein vaccine clinical trial in older adults
text:
Aug 10 Novavax Inc :
* Positive top-line data from phase 2 RSV F-protein vaccine clinical trial in older adults
* Trial showed statistically significant vaccine efficacy in prevention of symptomatic rsv disease in older adults
* RSV F vaccine was well-tolerated and fulfilled co's expectations of primary, secondary and exploratory objectives of trial Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
